## Requirements ##
Windows OS System

## Description ##
This is a batch file that creates a script for Windows DiskPart command. It allow the user to choose a Disk, then a 
Disk Partition and then removes the Disk Partition selected. It allows you to use it for any partition, however this 
was specifically used for removing Recovery Partitions.

## Notes ##
Usually it is better that the .bat be ran as Administrator in order to gain access to the disks.
